            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Pliseni<surplus>i</surplus>us Se<lb break="no" n="2"/><expan><abbr>veri</abbr><ex cert="low">a</ex>nus</expan> |(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XI <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audiae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>templum <expan><abbr>Lib</abbr><ex>eri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Pat</abbr><ex>ris</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>vetustate corrup<lb break="no" n="5"/>tum <expan><abbr>porticib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>adiect</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>restituit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Hederae. Z. 1: Marin u. a.: Pisen&amp;lt;t&amp;gt;ius. CIL III 1789 gibt die Kopie in Metkovic, Vid, wieder, CIL III 6363 und 8485 das Original in Ljubuški, Humac (Museum, Franziskanerkloster). (B): Škegro: Z. 2: [ex] leg(ione) XI Cl(audie) [p(ie) f(idelis)].</p>
            </div>
